data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Davenport, Florida. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and modern living. This home offers a spacious open-concept interior. Step inside and be greeted by an open-concept living space perfect for gatherings and entertaining guests. High ceilings and large windows fill the home with natural light. The downstairs Owners Suite has a jetted tub and tray lighting for a relaxing ambiance. Outside features a private courtyard for enjoying the Florida sunshine.    Nestled in a quiet, friendly neighborhood, this property is a true gem. This home gives you easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Disney World and other major attractions are just a short drive away, making this home an ideal vacation rental opportunity.  Residents enjoy access to community amenities, including a clubhouse, fitness center, and playground.  Take advantage of this opportunity to own a piece of Florida paradise. Schedule a showing today and make 2846 Bella Vista Drive your new home.
